OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGeorge Santos to step down 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom House committees      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Republican Congressman George Santos   
OL,6, will step down from serving on         
OL,7, committees in the US House of          
OL,8, Representatives.                       
OL,10,FThe 34-year-old has faced growing calls
OL,11,Fto resign after he admitted fabricating
OL,12,Fparts of his resume and biography since
OL,13,Fhis election in New York last year.    
OL,15,FHe was assigned to serve on two        
OL,16,Fcommittees despite the controversy.    
OL,18,FHe informed colleagues of his decision 
OL,19,Fat a closed-door meeting on Tuesday,   
OL,20,Fthe BBC's US partner CBS reports.      
